# ===================================
# Common .gitignore Patterns Reference
# ===================================
# Pattern                | Meaning
# ====================== | ========================================
# file.txt               | Ignore specific file
# *.log                  | Ignore all files with .log extension
# folder/                | Ignore entire folder
# folder/*.js            | Ignore .js files in folder only
# !important.log         | Exception - don't ignore this file
# **/node_modules        | Ignore node_modules in any directory
# ===================================

package-lock.json
